                <ul>
                    <li data-i18n="HotWeatherTip1">Stay hydrated - drink plenty of water</li>
                    <li data-i18n="HotWeatherTip2">Wear light-colored, loose-fitting clothing</li>
                    <li data-i18n="HotWeatherTip3">Avoid direct sunlight during peak hours (10 AM - 4 PM)</li>
